<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome to OmniBuzz Agency Admin</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .welcome-message {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #28a745;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .agency-name {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .features {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .feature-item {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .feature-item:before {
      content: "✓";
      color: #28a745;
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="welcome-message">Welcome to OmniBuzz Agency Admin!</div>
    <p>Congratulations on creating your agency: <span class="agency-name">{{agencyName}}</span></p>
  </div>

  <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
  
  <p>We're excited to welcome you as an Agency Administrator on OmniBuzz! Your account has been upgraded to give you full administrative control over your agency.</p>

  <div class="features">
    <h3>Your New Administrative Capabilities:</h3>
    <div class="feature-item">Manage your agency profile and settings</div>
    <div class="feature-item">Add and manage stations under your agency</div>
    <div class="feature-item">Assign staff members to your stations</div>
    <div class="feature-item">Monitor and manage bookings</div>
    <div class="feature-item">Access detailed analytics and reports</div>
  </div>

  <p>To get started with managing your agency, click the button below:</p>
  
  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Go to Agency Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help. You can reach us at {{supportEmail}}.</p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Thank you for choosing OmniBuzz for your transportation needs!</p>
    <p>© {{currentYear}} OmniBuzz. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>